While user research is invaluable, it does come with its own set of challenges. Here are some common obstacles and how to overcome them:

- **Recruitment Difficulties:** Finding the right participants can be tough. Consider using social media platforms or customer databases to reach potential users.

- **Bias in Data Collection:** Ensure your questions are neutral and unbiased to gather accurate data.

